Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.97,0:12:15.10,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}河住小太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.52,0:12:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘 長大了再來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.53,0:12:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我給妳調個適合妳的雞尾酒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.25,0:12:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 別說了 快切蘿卜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.72,0:12:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 簽好名了 去找其他工作人員吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.52,0:12:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.68,0:12:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.41,0:12:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還可以吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.41,0:12:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.54,0:12:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.27,0:12:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼風涼話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.86,0:12:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 就睜一隻眼閉一隻眼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.64,0:12:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.21,0:12:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.75,0:12:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是簽好名了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.62,0:12:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰說過不給你們簽名了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.19,0:12:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是說了說感想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.82,0:12:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.80,0:12:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點快點啦 不然要輸了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.50,0:12:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我記住了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.75,0:12:47.32,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}妖館步行拉力賽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.75,0:12:47.32,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}反之塚連勝 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.75,0:12:47.32,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}雪小路野薔薇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.52,0:13:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的工作人員都在哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.03,0:13:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們按順序去找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.15,0:13:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.19,0:13:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.40,0:13:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為要被踩了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.08,0:13:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好小
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.65,0:13:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是地精嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.29,0:13:33.01,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}女僕1
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.51,0:13:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在狹窄的地方打掃比較方便哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.85,0:13:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好小
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.59,0:13:44.03,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}妖館步行拉力賽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.59,0:13:44.03,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}雪小路野薔薇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.59,0:13:44.03,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}反之塚 連勝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.59,0:13:44.03,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}河住丈太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.59,0:13:44.03,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}河住小太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.59,0:13:44.03,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}小人村 千野
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.60,0:13:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦 我說妳小不是指胸啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.11,0:13:50.45,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}女僕2
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.91,0:13:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簽名？幹什麼？你們要做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.97,0:13:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可疑 不行 我才不會上當呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.78,0:13:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.37,0:14:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您工作繁忙之餘 還要讓您陪我們玩這種遊戲著實不忍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.95,0:14:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我們絕不是去做壞事 我向您保證
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.56,0:14:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以懇請您…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.58,0:14:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
