Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.86,0:14:10.82,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}河住 小太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.86,0:14:10.82,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}小人村 千野
