Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.37,0:14:56.79,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}河住 小太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.37,0:14:56.79,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}小人村 千野
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.37,0:14:56.79,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}童邊 步夢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.37,0:14:56.79,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}幸蛇 優二朗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.05,0:14:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 看上去好開心啊 也帶我一個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.25,0:15:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.27,0:15:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“開玩笑的啦”這種說法很古老呢哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.98,0:15:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是代溝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.22,0:15:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好開朗的人
